          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Home for the Brave Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Department of Housing and Urban Development Act to exclude veterans' service-connected disability or death benefits from income for purposes of the Department of Housing and Urban Development's assisted-housing programs determinations.</p>]]></text>
